            %a{:href => 'http://digitalcircle.org/events/belfast-ruby-testing-ruby'} BR-3: Testing Ruby
            %a{:href => "http://digitalcircle.org/events/belfast-ruby-an-introduction-to-spree-commerce"} BR-4: An Introduction to Spree Commerce
